data.description: WELCOME HOME! As you step through the front door of this property you're immediately struck by the sense of space and natural light. The high ceilings create an airy and inviting ambiance, designed to make a grand first impression. This stunning 3 bedroom property boasts modern decor and a backyard oasis, harmoniously blending contemporary design and outdoor tranquility. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable property your own! The master suite includes a private en-suite bathroom, offering a spa-like retreat for the homeowner. In addition to the master suite are 2 generously sized bedrooms. These versatile rooms provide the flexibility to cater to your unique lifestyle needs. Once outside, you will discover a picturesque outdoor setting with a meticulously landscaped garden and a cozy built in fire pit area, ideal for long Las Vegas evenings. *** Property is also available for Rent ***
